with version   stable 2.4.0
with version unstable 2.4.1cvs15
with base    curl libXaw libXxf86dga libXxf86vm libXv
with elect   XviD        --enable-xvid     --disable-xvid     for XviD divx codec support
with elect   alsa-lib    --enable-alsa     --disable-alsa     for alsa audio output
with elect   ffmpeg      --enable-ffmpeg   --disable-ffmpeg   for ffmpeg divx codec
with elect   jpeg        --enable-jpeg     --disable-jpeg     for jpeg snapshots
with elect   lame        --enable-lame     --disable-lame     for lame audio compression
with elect   libXinerama --enable-xinerama --disable-xinerama for xinerama multi-display support
with elect   lirc        --enable-lirc     --disable-lirc     to enable lirc remote control support
with elect   nxtvepg     ''                ''                 for TV program guide
#with elect   zvbi        --enable-zvbi     --disable-zvbi     for zvbi support

with role    video/television
with trait   x11
with trait   broke
with source    stable $SOURCEFORGE_URL xawdecode/01%20-%20XdTV/$VERSION/xdtv-$VERSION.tar.gz
with source  unstable $SOURCEFORGE_URL xawdecode/01%20-%20XdTV/$VERSION/xdtv-$VERSION.tar.gz
#     info good 20120716
with info    omit 20130101
with info    last 20070221
with info    home http://xawdecode.sourceforge.net
with info    cite 'television viewing software
It interacts with AleVT for Teletext and Nxtvepg for NextView.
It uses the video4linux API.
It can use deinterlacing filters and record video
files with the ffmpeg, xvid, and divx codecs.'
